<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; color:
      #333; padding: 0; margin: 0; } .container { max-width: 700px; margin: 30px
      auto; background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0
      5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header { text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #4caf50; padding-bottom: 10px; } .logo {
      max-width: 100px; margin-bottom: 10px; } .content { margin-top: 20px; }
      .content p { margin: 15px 0; } .highlight-box { background-color: #e8f5e9;
      padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; border-radius: 5px; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color:
      #777; } .signature { margin-top: 30px; } .signature p { margin: 4px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQHM4PYwztwggQ/company-logo_200_200/company-logo_200_200/0/1651251817154?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=6NcZAOrjh6W_s4nPrx4_9_o4HJS86hHm6iuKjvDe7ac"
          alt="Company Logo"
          class="logo"
        />
        <h1>Woodrock Softonic Pvt Ltd</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Date: <strong> {{offerLetterDate}}</strong></p>
        <p>To,</p>
        <p><strong>{{employeeName}}</strong><br />
          Email:
          {{employeeEmail}}</p>

        <p>Subject:
          <strong>Offer Letter - Woodrock Softonic Pvt Ltd</strong></p>

        <p>Hi There, I am pleased to present you an offer letter on behalf of
          Woodrock Softonic Pvt Ltd. We believe that your knowledge, skills and
          experience is an ideal fit for our team. We hope you are enjoying your
          role and going to make a significant contribution to the overall
          success of our company. Please take the time to review. It includes
          important details about your compensation, benefits and also the terms
          and conditions of your anticipated employment. Please acknowledge that
          you have received the mail and revert to me with the date and your
          signature. If in case you are not reverting to me within 24 hours I
          will consider it accepted.</p>
        <a
          href="https://netlifycon-hr.in/acknowledge/{{employeeEmail}}"
          style="display:inline-block; background:#4caf50; color:#fff; padding:10px 20px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:4px;"
          target="_blank"
        >
          Acknowledge Offer
        </a>

        <div class="signature">
          <p>Sincerely,</p>
          <img
            src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dri1mh3xh/image/upload/v1750698006/mhyrewrvtfgpqz21lfo7.jpg"
          />
          <p><strong>Simran Jha || HR Department</strong></p>
          <p><strong>Woodrock Softonic Pvt Ltd</strong></p>
          <p>Email:
            <a
              href="mailto:Simran.jha@woodrockgroup.in"
            >Simran.jha@woodrockgroup.in</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </body>

</html>